+
+[4] "OXPCIe958 PCI Express Bridge to Octal Serial Port", Oxford
+    Semiconductor, Inc., DS-0048, Feb 08, Section "950 Mode", p. 20
+
+Maciej W. Rozycki  <macro@orcam.me.uk>
